&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Valid driver&#39;s license with a clean driving record.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience in driving children or similar roles preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of traffic laws and safety regulations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to sit for extended periods of time while driving.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
