&lt;li&gt;Handle cash and credit card transactions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigate FC Cincinnati ticketing systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Additional duties include assisting with set up and putting away of ticket scanners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
