&lt;li&gt;Ability to handle cash and credit card transactions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must have basic math skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6+ months experience working as a concierge, event planner, waiter/waitress, housekeeper, or a role focused on providing excellent customer service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bilingual in English and Spanish is an added bonus&lt;/li&gt;
