&lt;p&gt;The Digital Video Producer will be directly responsible for producing content that furthers the FCC brand and its perspective into the sports landscape to grow and engage an audience through digital platforms. This position will work collaboratively with multiple departments to create engaging content on a daily basis with a focus on long-form and short-form video content.&lt;/p&gt;
